pyFormex is a program for generating, manipulating and operating on 
large geometrical models of 3D structures by sequences of mathematical
transformations.
Through its powerful scripting language, it is very useful for automated
and parametric design.
 
More information on the website: http://pyformex.berlios.de
or contact benedict.verhegghe@ugent.be

